{"tid":2083621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月1 維園見！","createTime":"2020-06-29T01:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:00:01.000Z","uid":8175,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"381e6074725f98c438a07f5f602ab0894a32700b","tid":2083621,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:07:44.000Z","msg":"2點鐘 維園見！"},{"pid":"5d59a0f5eeb24bda76c4baa1f05bc0f7cd3639a1","tid":2083621,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa1c6469d946c255d632c0d858c0a7a977c831bc","tid":2083621,"uid":50419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"七一見！<br />\n我支持靜默遊行<br />\n幾十萬人一言不發咁行"},{"pid":"a3b6afbf0668e48e77a65a426fba529ddb8eecc5","tid":2083621,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pBnePd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pBnePd.gif&h=d1d0a7c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2bc55ce6ece66f68d8baa4d3e2e6096172c8e","tid":2083621,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"七一見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8ZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=1fb787f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6db5c6853eb0e50209f6a08628e6ce7ea22d6fb5","tid":2083621,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"叫你戴個口罩去銅鑼灣行街都驚, 不如直接跪響雜種面前算啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2083595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2083595</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Gkn2SA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Gkn2SA.jpg&h=5fd8b4d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0b25ef08cf135222529ee683b05acc24f4a1416","tid":2083621,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673d5dc799d49a84870c084a8f41236aeb7b424a","tid":2083621,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409fad6bfb0ccbf31a9d28871d62d4ff85cb0eeb","tid":2083621,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85b387eb8b52ba1b9e0490e9274150f3d58ce08","tid":2083621,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa61d3c1335746700197b014f924195036229303","tid":2083621,"uid":149215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b410d8d151659237eff99d1c6c18a95e851f12","tid":2083621,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dbdc05f74eaf880f69287c42fa2b65533351e6","tid":2083621,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"7.1見"}]}